<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>New Lead | Thrive Nest Labs</title>

<style>
*{
margin:0;
padding:0;
box-sizing:border-box;
}

body{
background:#edf2f7;
font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,"Segoe UI",Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;
padding:40px 15px;
color:#1f2937;
}

.container{
max-width:760px;
margin:auto;
background:#ffffff;
border-radius:22px;
overflow:hidden;
box-shadow:0 20px 60px rgba(15,23,42,.15);
}

.hero{
background:linear-gradient(135deg,#2563eb 0%,#4f46e5 50%,#7c3aed 100%);
padding:50px 45px;
color:#fff;
}

.logo{
display:inline-block;
padding:10px 18px;
border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.25);
border-radius:50px;
font-size:13px;
font-weight:700;
letter-spacing:2px;
text-transform:uppercase;
background:rgba(255,255,255,.08);
margin-bottom:20px;
}

.hero h1{
font-size:34px;
font-weight:700;
margin-bottom:10px;
}

.hero p{
font-size:16px;
line-height:28px;
opacity:.95;
}

.content{
padding:40px;
}

.section{
margin-bottom:35px;
}

.section-title{
font-size:18px;
font-weight:700;
color:#111827;
margin-bottom:18px;
padding-bottom:10px;
border-bottom:2px solid #eef2ff;
}

.grid{
display:grid;
grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;
gap:18px;
}

.card{
background:#f8fafc;
border:1px solid #e5e7eb;
border-radius:14px;
padding:18px;
}

.label{
font-size:11px;
text-transform:uppercase;
letter-spacing:1.2px;
font-weight:700;
color:#64748b;
margin-bottom:8px;
}

.value{
font-size:16px;
font-weight:600;
color:#111827;
word-break:break-word;
line-height:24px;
}

.message-card{
background:#f8faff;
border-left:5px solid #4f46e5;
border-radius:14px;
padding:22px;
border-top:1px solid #e5e7eb;
border-right:1px solid #e5e7eb;
border-bottom:1px solid #e5e7eb;
}

.message-text{
font-size:16px;
line-height:30px;
color:#374151;
white-space:pre-wrap;
}

.cta{
margin-top:40px;
background:linear-gradient(135deg,#eff6ff,#eef2ff);
padding:25px;
border-radius:16px;
text-align:center;
border:1px solid #dbeafe;
}

.cta h3{
font-size:20px;
color:#1e3a8a;
margin-bottom:10px;
}

.cta p{
font-size:15px;
line-height:28px;
color:#475569;
}

.footer{
padding:35px;
background:#f8fafc;
text-align:center;
font-size:14px;
line-height:28px;
color:#64748b;
border-top:1px solid #e5e7eb;
}

.footer strong{
color:#111827;
}

.badge{
display:inline-block;
margin-top:15px;
padding:10px 18px;
background:#2563eb;
color:#fff;
border-radius:30px;
font-size:13px;
font-weight:600;
}

@media(max-width:700px){

.hero{
padding:35px 25px;
}

.hero h1{
font-size:28px;
}

.content{
padding:25px;
}

.grid{
grid-template-columns:1fr;
}

}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="container">

<div class="hero">

<div class="logo">
THRIVE NEST LABS
</div>

<h1>🚀 New Business Inquiry</h1>

<p>
Congratulations! A new potential client has contacted Thrive Nest Labs through your website.
Review the details below and respond promptly to maximize your conversion rate.
</p>

</div>

<div class="content">

<div class="section">

<div class="section-title">
👤 Client Information
</div>

<div class="grid">

<div class="card">
<div class="label">Full Name</div>
<div class="value"><%=name%></div>
</div>

<div class="card">
<div class="label">Company</div>
<div class="value"><%=company%></div>
</div>

<div class="card">
<div class="label">Country</div>
<div class="value"><%=country%></div>
</div>

<div class="card">
<div class="label">Website</div>
<div class="value"><%=website%></div>
</div>

</div>

</div>

<div class="section">

<div class="section-title">
📞 Contact Information
</div>

<div class="grid">

<div class="card">
<div class="label">Email Address</div>
<div class="value"><%=email%></div>
</div>

<div class="card">
<div class="label">Phone Number</div>
<div class="value"><%=mobile%></div>
</div>

<div class="card">
<div class="label">Preferred Contact</div>
<div class="value"><%=preferredContact%></div>
</div>

<div class="card">
<div class="label">Lead Source</div>
<div class="value"><%=source%></div>
</div>

</div>

</div>

<div class="section">

<div class="section-title">
💼 Project Details
</div>

<div class="grid">

<div class="card">
<div class="label">Requested Service</div>
<div class="value"><%=service%></div>
</div>

<div class="card">
<div class="label">Estimated Budget</div>
<div class="value"><%=budget%></div>
</div>

<div class="card">
<div class="label">Expected Timeline</div>
<div class="value"><%=timeline%></div>
</div>

</div>

</div>

<div class="section">

<div class="section-title">
📝 Project Requirements
</div>

<div class="message-card">

<div class="message-text">
<%=message%>
</div>

</div>

</div>

<div class="cta">

<h3>⚡ High Priority Lead</h3>

<p>
Businesses that respond within the first <strong>30–60 minutes</strong> are significantly more likely to convert inquiries into successful projects.
</p>

</div>

</div>

<div class="footer">

<strong>Thrive Nest Labs</strong><br>

Building Modern Digital Experiences, AI Solutions, Scalable SaaS Platforms & Enterprise Software.

<br><br>

This email was automatically generated from the Thrive Nest Labs website.

<div class="badge">
New Lead Notification
</div>

</div>

</div>

</body>
</html>
